-> It is Core Spring Project

-> we Have to Create Spring bean configuration file to create xml file 


* Spring SimpleJdbcTemplate 

-> Spring 3 JDBC supports the java 5 feature var-args (variable argument) and autoboxing by the help 
	of SimpleJdbcTemplate class.

-> SimpleJdbcTemplate class wraps the JdbcTemplate class and provides the update method where we can pass 
arbitrary number of arguments.

* Syntax of update method of SimpleJdbcTemplate class
-> int update(String sql,Object... parameters)  